data.description: This move-in ready ranch-style home with a bonus, located in the highly sought-after Heritage Farms Subdivision, is one you don't want to miss! Step outside to relax in your spacious, flat backyard, complete with a maintenance-free privacy fence and a screened-in porch. Inside, the home welcomes you with an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings in the living and dining areas, and a gas fireplace. Make your way towards the spacious kitchen, which boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a large pantry. The primary bedroom has a beautiful double tray ceiling with a fan, large walk-in closet, and a stunning bathroom containing double vanities, a garden tub, and a separate shower. Upstairs, discover a large bonus room that can serve as a perfect office or game room. Located only steps away from Cleveland Elementary/Middle School and just minutes away from the White Oak Shopping Center. Freshly painted throughout the entire home!''
